"""
PART III Income

15. Income for the purposes of the Act

(1)

Editorial note: current text valid from 2025-03-21.

For the purposes of section 15(1)(e) (income), all social security benefits are prescribed except—

(k)

Christmas bonus payable under Part X of the 1992 Act;
"""

relevant_benefit_is_social_security_benefit_15_1_fact:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean

relevant_benefit_is_christmas_bonus_payable_under_part_x_of_1992_act_15_1_k_fact:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean

christmas_bonus_payable_under_part_x_of_1992_act_is_not_prescribed_income_15_1_k:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean
    from 2025-03-21:
        if relevant_benefit_is_social_security_benefit_15_1_fact: relevant_benefit_is_christmas_bonus_payable_under_part_x_of_1992_act_15_1_k_fact else: false
